## 🎯 方案 B：浏览器控制台 JavaScript（最简单）

1. **打开** https://clawhub.com/publish
2. **按 F12** 打开开发者工具
3. **切换到 Console 标签**
4. **粘贴以下代码，回车**：

```javascript
// 自动填写并提交表单
const skills = [
  {name: "password-generator", desc: "Generate secure passwords"},
  {name: "csv-processor", desc: "Process CSV files"},
  {name: "markdown-formatter", desc: "Format Markdown"}
];

let i = 0;
function publishNext() {
  if (i >= skills.length) { alert("Done!"); return; }
  const s = skills[i];
  document.querySelector('input[name="name"]').value = s.name;
  document.querySelector('textarea[name="description"]').value = s.desc;
  document.querySelector('input[name="github_url"]').value = `https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/${s.name}_SKILL.md`;
  document.querySelector('button[type="submit"]').click();
  i++;
  setTimeout(() => { window.location.href = "https://clawhub.com/publish"; setTimeout(publishNext, 2000); }, 3000);
}
publishNext();
```

